Ki-tok-tou5 Na7 Hoan7 Choe7
Ki-tok-tou5 na7 hoan7 choe7, i2-au7 oe7 chaiN2-iuN7? I oe7 biat8-bo5, a2-si7 eng2-oan2 tim5-lun5? Siong7-te3 beh khi3-sak i a2-si7 iu5-goan5 choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5? Na7 iu5-goan5 choe3 I e5 kiaN2-ji5, Siong7-te3 beh chaiN2-iuN7 tui3-thai7 i? Goa2 beh eng7 chit 6 hang7 su7 lai5 in3-tap chit-e5 bun7-toe5:
1. Ki-tok-tou5 Bo5 Koh Ke3-siok8 Hoan7 Choe7.
Ki-tok-tou5 teh kiaN5 kong-gi7, u7 kong-gi7 e5 seng-oah8. “KiN3-na7 toa3 ti7 I e5, bo5 hoan7 choe7; kiN3-na7 hoan7 choe7 e5, be7-bat khoaN3-kiN3 I, ia7 m7-bat I,......Hoan7 choe7 e5 si7 tui3 Mou5-kui2 chhut,......KiN3-na7 tui3 Siong7-te3 siN e5 chiu7 bo5 hoan7 choe7, in-ui7 I e5 cheng2 tng5-tng5 tiam3-ti7 i; i ia7 boe7 hoan7 choe7, in-ui7 i si7 tui3 Siong7-te3 siN e5. Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5 kap Mou5-kui2 e5 kiaN2-ji5 tui3 an2-ni hian2-beng5” (I Iok-han7 3:6, 8~10). Ti7 i2-siong7 chiah-e5 Seng3-keng-chat lai7-bin7 e5 tong7-su5, long2 si7 hian7-chai7 chin3-heng5 sek, bo5 koh soa3-chiap hoan7 choe7 a2-si7 ke3-siok8 teh hoan7-choe7. Choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5 bo5 koh ke3-siok8 hoan7 choe7, in-ui7 i bo5 tiam3-ti7 choe7-ok e5 lai7-bin7; chiu7-si7 Ki-tok-tou5 bo5 koh ke3-siok8 ti7 choe7-ok e5 lai7-bin7 hong3-chhiong3, ke3-siok8 hoan7 choe7. Che m7 si7 i seng-oah8 e5 tek8-tiong5, oaN7 oe7 lai5 kong2, i bo5 koh-chai3 tit8-tit8 hoan7 choe7. I na7-si7 koh-chai3 ke3-siok8 tit8-tit8 hoan7 choe7, chiu7 m7 si7 tui3 Siong7-te3 siN e5, i iu5-goan5 siok8 ti7 Sat-tan.
2.Chong2-si7 I Oe7 Poah8-to2 Ham7-loh8 Choe7-ok
“Goa2 e5 soe3-kiaN2 ah, goa2 sia2 chiah-e5 hou7 lin2, si7 beh hou7 lin2 bo5 hoan7 choe7. Na7 u7 lang5 hoan7 choe7, chiu7 ti7 Pe7 e5 bin7-cheng5 lan2 u7 Po2-hui7-su, chiu7-si7 gi7-lang5 Ia5-sou Ki-tok; I ui7-tioh8 lan2 e5 choe7, choe3 ban2-hoe5 e5 che3” (I Iok-han7 2:1~2). Ti7 chia kong2 chin beng5, Ki-tok-tou5 m7-bian2 tek-khak tioh8 hoan7-choe7; i m7-bian2 kou3-i3 hoan7 choe7, a2-si7 khi3 choe3 ka-ki7 i2-keng chai e5 m7-tioh8. I tui3 choe7-ok oe7 thang tit-tioh8 thau2-pang3, m7-bian2 poah8-to2 ham7-loh8 ti7 choe7-ok.
Na7-si7, ui7-tioh8 hoan7 choe7 e5 Ki-tok-tou5, Siong7-te3 u7 chun2-pi7. Siong7-te3 kong2: “Na7 u7 lang5 hoan7 choe7”, ti7 chia chin beng5 ka7 lan2 kong2, Ki-tok-tou5 ia7 oe7 hoan7 choe7, Ki-tok-tou5 ia7 oe7 poah8-to2, ham7-loh8 ti7 choe7-ok. Chong2-si7 hoan7 choe7 m7 si7 chit8-e5 Ki-tok-tou5 ti7 seng-oah8 tiong cheng3-siong5 e5 piau2-hian7, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 chi2-lam5-chiam tioh8 ki2 lam5--si3, kho2-sioh ia7 oe7 siu7 pat8-mih8 e5 eng2-hiong2, chiam7-si5 oe7 ki2 pat8 hong-hiong3; chong2-si7 kau3 be2 i tek-khak oe7 koh ki2 pak--si3. Ki-tok-tou5 ia7 chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni, i bo5 ke3-siok8 teh hoan7 choe7, na7-si7 i kiam2-chhai2 oe7 poah8-to2 ham7-loh8 ti7 choe7-ok. I na7 hoan7 choe7, i u7 chit8-ui7 Po2-hui7-su, Chu2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok, I chiaN5-choe3 un-tian2 e5 cho7-ui7, ban2-hoe5 e5 che3, i e5 choe7 chiu7 oe7 tit-tioh8 sia3-bian2.
Chit-e5 koan-he7, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 iuN5 kap ti. Chit8-chiah iuN5 bo5 tiuN-ti5 chiu7 poah8-loh8 ti7 chit8-e5 lou7-kou5-be5 khut. Na7-si7 ti chiu7 m7 si7 an2-ni, i chit8 e7 khoaN3-tioh8 lou7-kou5-be5 khut, chiu7 tit8-tit8 chong5-khi3, chin hoaN-hi2 kam-goan7 thiau3 jip8-khi3. Kiat-ko2, chit-chiah iuN5 chiu7 koaN2-kin2 tui3 lou7-kou5-be5 khut pe5 khi2-lai5, liau2-au7, chiu7 chin7 sou2 oe7 beh li7-khui hit-e5 khut hng7-hng7; na7-si7 hit-chiah ti chiu7 bo5 siuN7 beh pe5 khi2-lai5, i ai3 tiam3-ti7 hit lai7-bin7. In-ui7 che si7 i e5 pun2-seng3, i ai3 la5-sam5 e5 lou7-kou5-be5.
Sin3-tou5 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 iuN5, kiam2-chhai2 ti7 bo5 keng2-seng2 e5 si5 poah8-to2 ham7-loh8 ti7 choe7-ok, chong2-si7 i sui5-si5 li7-khui hit e5 choe7-ok, jin7 i e5 choe7, koh chit8-pai2 tng2-lai5 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5, kiu5 Chu2 Ia5-sou e5 po2-huih ka7 i soe2 chheng-khi3. I an2-ni choe3, in-ui7 i e5 pun2-seng3 him-bou7 kong-gi7, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 hit-chiah iuN5 ai3 chheng-khi3.
Be7 tit-kiu3 e5 lang5 , chiu7 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 hit chiah ti ai3 tiam3-ti7 lou7-kou5-be5 khut, ko7--lai5 ko7--khi3, che si7 i e5 pun2-seng3; choe7-jin5 ia7 si7 siang7-khoan2. An2-ni, li2 chiu7 oe7 thang khoaN3-chhut iuN5 kap ti pun2-seng3 e5 cheng-chha. Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5 kap Mou5-kui2 e5 kiaN2-ji5, ia7 oe7 thang tui3 an2-ni hun-piat8. In kiam2-chhai2 long2 ham7-loh8 ti7 choe7-ok e5 lai7-bin7, na7-si7 chi2-u7 chit8-e5 oe7 ke3-siok8 tiam3-ti7 choe7-ok. Ki-tok-tou5 boe7 ke3-siok8 hoan7 choe7, i bo5 ai3 tiam3-ti7 lou7-kou5-be5 khut e5 lai7-bin7. Li2 poah8-to2 hoan7-choe7, boe7 ti3-kau3 piN3-choe3 chit8-e5 bo5 sin3 e5 goa7-pang lang5 . Chong2-si7 li2 na7 iu5-goan5 tiam3-ti7 choe7-ok, chiu7 cheng3-beng5 li2 si7 chit8-e5 bo5 sin3 Siong7-te3 e5 goa7-pang lang5 .
3. Ki-tok-tou5 Na7 Hoan2 Hoe2, Siong7-te3 Boe7 Khi3-sak I.
“KiN3-na7 Pe7 sou2 hou7 Goa2 e5, beh long2 chiu7-kun7 Goa2; chiu7-kun7 Goa2 e5 lang5 , Goa2 koat-toan3 bo5 khi3-sak i” (Iok-han7 6:37). Siong7-te3 choat8-tui3 boe7 khi3-sak i, bo5 hou7 i choe3 I e5 kiaN2-ji5. Siong7-te3 iu5-goan5 beh khoan2-thai7 i choe3 ka-ki7 e5 kiaN2-ji5. TaN Siong7-te3 beh chaiN2-iuN7 khoan2-thai7 I e5 kiaN2-ji5? “Siat-su2 i e5 kiaN2-sun pang3-sak Goa2 e5 lut8-hoat; Bo5 kiaN5 goa2 e5 hoat-tou7; Poe7-biu7 Goa2 e5 lut8-le7, Bo5 siu2 Goa2 e5 kai3-beng7; Goa2 chiu7 beh eng7 koaiN2-a2 chek-hoat8 in e5 ke3-sit; Eng7 piN chek-hoat8 in e5 choe7-ok. Chong2-si7 Goa2 tek-khak bo5 chiong Goa2 e5 chu5-ai3 it-chin7 tui3 i siu-hoe5; Iah8 tek-khak bo5 hou7 Goa2 e5 sin3-sit8 hoe3-bo5. Goa2 tek-khak bo5 sit Goa2 e5 iok; Iah8 bo5 koe2-oaN7 Goa2 e5 chhui3 sou2 kong2--e5” (Si-phian 89:30~34). Lan2 thang khoaN3 chhut Siong7-te3 beh ka3-si7 in, chek-hoat8 in, chong2-si7 tek-khak bo5 hoe3-bo5 I e5 sin3-sit8.
Choe3 lang5 e5 kiaN2-ji5, na7 ui5-poe7 pe7-bu2, chiu7 tioh8 siu7 pe7-bu2 e5 chek-hoat8; chek-hoat8 e5 bok8-tek, chiu7-si7 ui7-tioh8 beh kai2-cheng3 kiaN2-ji5 e5 ke3-sit, ui7-tioh8 ai3 kiaN2-ji5 siu7 kam2-tong7 kiaN5 chiaN3-lou7, sou2-i2 chiah eng7 koaiN2 phah in. Siong7-te3 ia7 an2-ni, I e5 chek-hoat8 kiam2-chhai2 chin giam5, lang5 chiu7 siu7 kan-khou2, chong2-si7 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 pe7-bu2 teh chek-hoat8 kiaN2-ji5, na7 u7 su-iau3 iah8 tioh8 eng7 chhe5 lai5 phah. Siong7-te3 ia7 beh an2-ni choe3. Pe7-bu2 choat8-tui3 boe7 koaN2 kiaN2-ji5 chhut mng5, kio3 in eng2-oan2 m7-thang koh tng2-lai5. In-ui7 in long2 si7 pe7-bu2 e5 kiaN2-ji5, long2 si7 kang7 chit8 ke lang5 , sou2-i2 chiu7 eng7 giam5-hat e5 ka3-si7, chek-hoat8, lai5 kai2-cheng3 in e5 m7-tioh8.
“Goa2 beh choe3 i e5 Pe7, i beh choe3 Goa2 e5 kiaN2; i na7 hoan7-choe7, Goa2 beh eng7 lang5 e5 koaiN2, se3-kan lang5 e5 piN, chek-tok i. chong2-si7 Goa2 e5 chu5-ai3 bo5 beh li7-khui i” (II Sat-bou2-jiN2 7:14~15). Siong7-te3 si7 lan2 e5 ThiN-pe7, lan2 si7 I e5 kiaN2-ji5, lan2 na7 hoan7 choe7, I chiu7 beh ka3-si7 lan2, I beh eng7 koaiN2, eng7 piN chek-hoat8 lan2, lan2 tioh8 jim2-siu7 I e5 keng2-kai3. I e5 chu5-ai3 boe7 li7-khui lan2, lan2 iu5-goan5 si7 I e5 kiaN2-ji5.
4. Kau-poe5 U7 Toan7-choat8, Hoan2-hoe2 Chiu7 Koh Hoe5-hok8.
“Lan2 na7 jin7 lan2 e5 choe7, I si7 chin-sit8 kong-gi7, beh sia3-bian2 lan2 e5 choe7, soe2-tu5 lan2 long2-chong2 e5 put-gi7” (I Iok-han7 1:9). Lan2 chit8-e7 hoan7 choe7, lan2 kap Siong7-te3 e5 kau-poe5 chiu7 toan7-choat8. Lan2 na7 beh hoe5-hok8 chit-e5 kau-poe5, chiu7 tioh8 jin7-choe7 kiu5 sia3-bian2, an2-ni chiah oe7 thang kap Siong7-te3 ho5-ho2.
U7 choe7-choe7 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5, bo5 teh kap I kau-poe5, in e5 seng-oah8 bo5 sun7-than3 I, chiu7 sit-loh8 hoaN-hi2 khoai3-lok8 kap peng5-an. In-ui7 in sou2 choe3 e5, m7-si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 hoaN-hi2 e5, in u7 kou-hu7 Siong7-te3 , ti7 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5 hoan7 choe7. Chong2-si7 I iau2-ku2 teh theng3-hau7 in jin7-choe7 hoan2-hoe2; hou7 in kap Siong7-te3 e5 koan-he7 oe7 thang hoe5-hok8. Chit-e5 kau-poe5 toan7-choat8 e5 si5, lan2 e5 ki5-to2 koat-toan3 boe7 tit-tioh8 sia3-bian2 chiah oe7 thang hoe5-hok8. Lan2 na7 jin7-choe7, I chiu7 chek-si5 sia3-bian2 lan2. “I e5 KiaN2 Ia5-sou e5 huih soe2-tu5 lan2 long2-chong2 e5 choe7” (I Iok-han7 1:7).
Hoan7-choe7 e5 lang5 , chiu7-si7 kiaN5 m7-tioh8 lou7, i eng-kai koh tng2-lai5 kiaN5 chiaN3-lou7 chiah tioh8; na7-si7 i tioh8 jin7 ka-ki7 e5 m7-tioh8 koh tng2-lai5, chiah oe7 thang kiaN5 chiaN3-lou7. Li2 bo5 khoai3-lok8 e5 goan5-in, kiam2-chhai2 si7 in-ui7 li2 bo5 kap Siong7-te3 kau-poe5, li2 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5, na7-si7 li2 kap I kau-poe5 u7 that-gai7, ti3-kau3 toan7-choat8.
5. Ki-tok-tou5 Tioh8 Ka-ki7 Hun-piat8, Na7 Bo5, Siong7-te3 Beh Sim2-phoann3.
“An2-ni, hoan7-na7 chiah8 Chu2 e5 piaN2, a2-si7 lim Chu2 e5 poe, bo5 hap8-gi5 e5, si7 kou-hu7 ChU2 e5 seng-khu kap huih. Na7-si7 lang5 tioh8 ka-ki7 seng2-chhat, chiah thang chiah8 chit e5 piaN2, lim chit e5 poe. lang5 bo5 hun-piat8 Chu2 e5 seng-khu lai5 lim-chiah8, chiu7-si7 tui3 lim-chiah8 ka-ki7 chhu2 sim2-phoaN3. Sou2-i2 lin2 tiong-kan soe-lan2 e5, phoa3-piN7 e5, choe7-choe7; si2 e5 ia7 bo5 chio2. Lan2 na7 ka-ki7 sim2-mng7, chiu7 bo5 siu7 sim2-phoaN3. Chong2-si7 lan2 siu7 sim2-phoaN3, si7 hou7 Chu2 sou2 keng2-kai3, bian2-tit kap se3-kan lang5 tang5 siu7 teng7-choe7” (I Ko-lim5-to 11:27~32).
Bo5 hap8-gi5 e5, chiu7-si7 sin3-chia2 chai-iaN2 u7 choe7, na7-si7 bo5 jin7-choe7. Lan2 tioh8 jin7-choe7 tu5-khi3 phaiN2-tai7, tit-tioh8 Chu2 e5 po2-huih soe2 chheng-khi3 kap sia3-bian2, lan2 chiah thang siu7 Seng3-chhan. Siong7-te3 hoan-hu3 sin3-chia2 tioh8 ka-ki7 seng2-chhat hun-piat8, na7 m7 an2-ni choe3, chiu7-si7 tui3 lim-chiah8 ka-ki7 chhu2 sim2-phoaN3, i3-su3 chiu7-si7 beh siu7 chek-hoat8.
Ui7-tioh8 an2-ni, Siong7-te3 kong2, I e5 kiaN2-ji5 u7 choe7-choe7 lang5 soe-lan2 koh phoa3-piN7, si2 e5 ia7 bo5 chio2. Goa2 bo5 kong2 sou2 u7 e5 phoa3-piN7, long2 si7 tui3 choe7-ok lai5, chong2-si7 kiam2-chhai2 u7 choe7-choe7 e5 soe-lan2 kap phoa3-piN7, si7 tui3 m7 jin7-choe7 lai5 in2-khi2 e5; kiam2-chhai2 li2 sit-giap8 ia7-si7 an2-ni. In-ui7 Siong7-te3 eng7 chiah-e5 khian5-keng3 teh tui3-hu3, sim2-phoaN3 kap chek-hoat8 li2, I ai3 in2-chhoa7 li2 to3-tng2 koh chit8 pai2 kap I kau-poe5; li2 na7 iau2-ku2 bo5 beh jin7-choe7, bo5 eng5-kng I, koh hou7 I kian3-siau3, I kiam2-chhai2 beh chhu2 li2 e5 siN3-mia7.
Siong7-te3 u7 ka7 lan2 kong2, lan2 na7 ka-ki7 sim2-mng7, chiu7 bo5 siu7 sim2-phoaN3. OaN7 oe7 lai5 kong2, lan2 na7 beh jin7-choe7, hoan2-hoe2, tit-tioh8 I e5 sia3-bian2, I chiu7 bo5 beh keng2-kai3 lan2. TaN Siong7-te3 koh ka7 lan2 kong2 chin beng5, I sim2-phoaN3 lan2 e5 si5, chiu7 chek-hoat8 lan2, in-ui7 lan2 si7 I e5 kiaN2-ji5, I m7-ai3 lan2 kap se3-kan lang5 saN-kap siu7 teng7-choe7. Ki3-jian5 choe3 I e5 kiaN2-ji5, I chiu7 beh an2-ni khoan2-thai7 lan2, lan2 tioh8 jim2-siu7 Siong7-te3 e5 keng2-kai3. Li2 e5 siu7-khou2, kiam2-chhai2 si7 Siong7-te3 e5 sim2-phoaN3, chek-hoat8, chi2-u7 jin7-choe7, kap Siong7-te3 ho5-ho2 chiah bian2 siu7 I keng2-kai3.
6. Kiann5 Ti7 Kng-beng5, Tak8-jit8 Tit-tioh8 Chheng-khi3.
“Tok8-tok8 lan2 na7 kiaN5 ti7 kng-beng5, chhin-chhiuN7 I tiam3-ti7 kng-beng5, chiu7 lan2 saN-kap kau-poe5, ia7 I e5 KiaN2 Ia5-sou e5 huih soe2-tu5 lan2 long2-chong2 e5 choe7” (I Iok-han7 1:7). Lan2 tioh8 sun7-hok8 Chu2, li7-khui it-chhe3 lan2 sou2 chai e5 put-gi7 kap choe7-ok, chiau3 Siong7-te3 e5 chi2-i3 lai5 oah8. An2-ni chiah oe7 thang kiaN5 ti7 kng-beng5. Lan2 na7 hoan7 choe7, chiu7 bo5 kiaN5 ti7 kng-beng5, in-ui7 lan2 chai, choe7 si7 m7-tioh8, put-gi7. lang5 na7 kiaN5 ti7 kng-beng5, chiu7 jit8-jit8 tui3 i e5 choe7 tit-tioh8 soe2-chheng.
Ti7 Seng3-keng lai7 u7 ki3-chai3, Chu2 Ia5-sou beh soe2 Pi2-tek e5 kha, Pi2-tek ku7-choat8. Ia5-sou ka7 i kong2, I na7 bo5 soe2 i e5 kha, i chiu7 kap Chu2 bo5 kan-siap8. Pi2-tek chiu7 kiu5 Chu2 ka7 i soe2 choan5 seng-khu. Ia5-sou ka7 i kong2, lang5 na7 soe2 chit8 pai2, chiu7-si7 soe2-ek8 liau2------oaN7 oe7 kong2, i na7 teng5-thau5-siN tit-kiu3------i chiu7 m7-bian2 koh soe2 choan5 seng-khu. Chong2-si7 i e5 kha in-ui7 kiaN5-lou7 chiu7 bak-tioh8 thou5-hun2 la5-sam5, tioh8 ai3 soe2, sou2-i2 Ia5-sou tit8-tit8 beh soe2 Pi2-tek e5 kha.
TaN li2 i2-keng tit-kiu3, i2-keng soe2-ek8, choan5 seng-khu long2 chheng-khi3, teng5-thau5-siN choe3 Siong7-te3 e5 kiaN2-ji5, chong2-si7 li2 chit8-si3-lang5 seng-oah8 ti7 chit-e5 se3-kan, chiu7 oe7 hou7 khoaN3 oe7-tioh8, khoaN3 boe7-tioh8 e5 u3-oe3 phah la5-sam5, sou2-i2 li2 put-si5 tioh8 soe2 chheng-khi3. Siong7-te3 i2-keng thoe3 lan2 pi7-pan7, chiu7-si7 I e5 KiaN2 Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 po2-huih, beh si5-siong5 soe2 chheng-khi3 lan2 long2-chong2 e5 choe7. Chong2-si7 li2 tioh8 kiaN5 ti7 kng-beng5 e5 tiong-kan, tioh8 choe3 cheng3-tong koh si7 ho2 e5 tai7-chi3, m7-thang kou3-i3 khi3 choe3 m7-tioh8.
Goa2 bat khou2-khng3 li2, na7 hoan7 choe7 tioh8 sui5-si5 kau3 Siong7-te3 e5 bin7-cheng5; li2 m7 eng-kai hoan7 choe7, chong2-si7 li2 kiam2-chhai2 oe7 ham7-loh8 ti7 choe7-ok, na7 an2-ni, li2 tioh8 chek-si5 hoan2-hoe2, kiu5 Chu2 sia3-bian2. Kap Siong7-te3 e5 kau-poe5 sui-jian5 bat u7 that-gai7 lai5 toan7-choat8, chong2-si7 li2 na7 jin7-choe7, tit-tioh8 I e5 po2-huih soe2 chheng-khi3, chiu7 koh chit8 pai2 hoe5-hok8 kap Siong7-te3 e5 kau-poe5. Li2 hian7-chai7 tioh8 hun-piat8 ka-ki7, Siong7-te3 chiu7 m7-bian2 sim2-phoaN3. Chong2-si7 li2 na7 kiaN5 ti7 kng-beng5, Ia5-sou Ki-tok e5 po2-huih, chiu7 beh si5-siong5 soe2-chheng li2 long2-chong2 e5 choe7.
Kam2-sia7 Siong7-te3 , I ka7 lan2 pi7-pan7 tak8-hang7 long2 kau3-giah8. I chai-iaN2 lan2 oe7 hoan7 choe7; lan2 hou7 I sit-bang7 e5 si5, I bo5 khi3-sak lan2, koh khoan2-thai7 lan2 choe3 I e5 kiaN2-ji5, choe3 I ka-teng5 e5 lang5 . Lan2 e5 choe7 oe7 thang tit-tioh8 sia3-bian2, kap chu2 e5 kau-poe5 oe7 thang hoe5-hok8, lan2 ia7 oe7 thang kap Siong7-te3 saN-kap kiaN5. An2-ni, I e5 peng5-an, hoaN-hi2, khoai3-lok8, chiu7 tiam3-ti7 lan2 e5 sim-lai7, lan2 chiu7 kap hiaN-ti7 chi2-be7, i2-kip8 Chu2 Ia5-sou saN-kap kau-poe5.
